{"comments":"Motion and animation style tokens\n\nThis module provides type-safe tokens for CSS transitions and animations,\nbridging the Schema motion primitives to Tailwind CSS classes.\n\n## Duration Tokens\n\nDuration represents how long animations/transitions take:\n- `Instant` (0ms) - Immediate, no transition\n- `Fast` (75ms) - Micro-interactions, hover states\n- `Quick` (150ms) - Snappy UI feedback\n- `Normal` (300ms) - Standard transitions\n- `Slow` (500ms) - Deliberate animations\n- `Slower` (700ms) - Complex state changes\n- `Slowest` (1000ms) - Page transitions, loading states\n\n## Easing Tokens\n\nEasing defines the acceleration curve:\n- `Linear` - Constant speed\n- `EaseIn` - Start slow, end fast\n- `EaseOut` - Start fast, end slow\n- `EaseInOut` - Slow at both ends\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Style.Motion as Motion\nimport Hydrogen.Style.Css (cx)\n\n-- Basic transition\ncx [ Motion.transition Motion.All\n   , Motion.duration Motion.Normal\n   , Motion.easing Motion.EaseOut\n   ]\n-- \"transition-all duration-300 ease-out\"\n\n-- Quick hover feedback\ncx [ Motion.transition Motion.Colors\n   , Motion.duration Motion.Quick\n   ]\n-- \"transition-colors duration-150\"\n\n-- Animated element\ncx [ Motion.animate Motion.Spin ]\n-- \"animate-spin\"\n\n-- Respect user preferences\ncx [ Motion.motionSafe (Motion.duration Motion.Normal)\n   , Motion.motionReduce (Motion.duration Motion.Instant)\n   ]\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[130,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Style/Motion.purs","start":[130,3]},"title":"Instant"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[131,9],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Style/Motion.purs","start":[131,3]},"title":"Fast"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[132,10],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Style/Motion.purs","start":[132,3]},"title":"Quick"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[133,11],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Style/Motion.purs","start":[133,3]},"title":"Normal"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[134,9],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Style/Motion.purs","start":[134,3]},"title":"Slow"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[135,11],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Style/Motion.purs","start":[135,3]},"title":"Slower"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[136,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Style/Motion.purs","start":[136,3]},"title":"Slowest"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[137,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Style/Motion.purs","start":[137,3]},"title":"DurationMs"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Style","Motion"],"Duration"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[139,42],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Style/Motion.purs","start":[139,1]},"title":"eqDuration"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Style","Motion"],"Duration"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[150,54],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Style/Motion.purs","start":[141,1]},"title":"showDuration"}],"comments":"Duration scale for transitions and animations\n\nSemantic durations aligned with UX best 